;
INUMBER 1617
NAME 32
WEIGHT 4
VOLUME 4
BOW_WEAPON
PARAMETER1 14
PARAMETER2 1804
WORN_DON
SUBSTANCE INDESTRUCTABLE
VARIABLE SHOOTER
IFSEEK 180
	IFVERB CONCENTRATE -1
		IFVAR ITEMVAL5 ! TIM
			ECHO PLAYER May your aim be true.
			SPELL 512 10
			ECHO Player Let your enemies not harm you.
			SPELL 133 10
			EQUAL ITEMVAL5 TIM
		ENDIF
	ENDIF
ENDIF
IFVERB LISTEN -1
	ECHO PLAYER For you and only for you I shall reveal the full extent of my powers. If you have need of protection and steady hands you have only to concentrate on me. Should you need your health restored player polish me to a high luster. If you ever need light to see my attention by tapping me.
ENDIF
IFVERB WEAR -1
	ECHO PLAYER You sling the bow over your shoulder.
ENDIF
IFPREVERB GIVE -1
	ECHO PLAYER I am for you and no other. I shall be touched by no other hand.
	ECHO OTHERS %n gets a glazed look for a moment and then nods his head absently.
        CLEARVERB
ENDIF
IFPREVERB DROP -1
	ECHO PLAYER I shall not leave your hand we are as one now.
	ECHO OTHERS %n looks like he is about to set the bow down and then changes his mind.
        CLEARVERB
ENDIF
IFPREVERB PUT -1
	ECHO PLAYER No, I will not be seperated from you.
	ECHO OTHERS %n grasps the bow tightly.
	CLEARVERB
ENDIF
IFITEM -1 WIELDED
	IFVERB LOAD -1
		ECHO PLAYER As the bow is loaded the arrow shimmers magically.
	ENDIF
ENDIF
IFVERB RUB -1
	ECHO PLAYER As you polish the bow lovingly, it glows a soft blue and speaks to you:
	ECHO PLAYER Let my power heal thy wounds.
	ECHO OTHERS %n polishes %a to a high luster and a soft blue glow surrounds %i.
	EQUAL ROUNDTIME 21
	SPELL 318
ENDIF
IFVERB TAP -1
	ECHO ALL The bow flares with a brilliant blue light.
	SPELL 113 20
ENDIF
IFPREVERB PULL -1
          IFITEM -1 WIELDED
                 CLEARVERB
                 ECHO PLAYER You raise %a in salute.
                 ECHO OTHERS %N raises %a in salute.
          ENDIF
ENDIF
