;
; glowworm
INUMBER 1631
NAME 1378
MISC
WEIGHT 1
VOLUME 1
LIGHTABLE
DYE
PARAMETER3 943
*DESCRIPTION_START EXAM
The glowworm is about two inches long. Its skin is pale green with bright  spots of phosphorescence randomly scattered across its back and sides. With legs in the front and back, it walks like an inchworm, bending itself into a u-shape and then straightening out again.
*DESCRIPTION_END
IFPREVERB UNLIGHT -1
	ECHO PLAYER You'd have to kill it to do that.
	CLEARVERB
ENDIF
IFPREVERB LIGHT -1
	ECHO PLAYER It's already glowing as much as it can.
	CLEARVERB
ENDIF
IFPREVERB PINCH -1
	ECHO PLAYER You smash the glowworm into a luminous mess.
	ECHO OTHERS %N smashes a glowworm into a luminous mess.
	APPEAR %N has smashed glowworm all over %h hands.
	REMOVEITEM -1
	CLEARVERB
ENDIF
IFTOUCH -1
	RANDOM dummy1 1 10 0
	IFVAR dummy1 = 5
		ECHO PLAYER The glowworm looks like it's drying out a bit.
	ENDIF
	IFVAR dummy1 = 9
		ECHO PLAYER The glowworm, too long removed from its natural environment, dies. Its dry husk blows away on the wind.
		ECHO OTHERS %N's glowworm, too long removed from its habitat, dies. Its dry husk blows away on the wind.
		REMOVEITEM -1
		CLEARVERB
	ENDIF
ENDIF
