INUMBER 573
NAME 1551
WEIGHT 1
VOLUME 1
FOOD
PARAMETER1 4
IFPREVERB LOOK -1
	CLEARVERB
	ECHO PLAYER The cupcake is a small confection of chocolatey goodness.
ENDIF
