INUMBER 1538
NAME 1435
WEIGHT 1
VOLUME 1
SKIN
SUBSTANCE BRITTLE
*DESCRIPTION_START EXAMINE
Within the clear gem you can see the tortured soul of one of
Soultaker's previous victims.
*DESCRIPTION_END
VARIABLE gem
IFVERB CONCENTRATE -1
  CLEARVERB
  ECHO PLAYER You feel yourself locked in a struggle for an immortal\
soul!
  ECHO OTHERS %N's body goes rigid as %s matches %h will against that\
of the confining gem.
  RANDOM gem 1 100 0
  ADD gem WIL
    IFVAR gem => 175
      ECHO PLAYER The gem shatters into millions of multi-colored shards!
      ECHO ALL The gem, once a prison, shatters, and releases the captive\
soul! Casting a glance of the deepest gratitude at you the soul ascends to\
its final resting place.
      AWARD 61 4000
      ELSE
      ECHO PLAYER The gem resists your efforts! Pain lances through your\
head!
      DAMAGE BODYONLY 40 %N grabs %h head, moaning with pain.
    ENDIF
    REMOVEITEM -1
ENDIF
