INUMBER 1694
NAME 470
WORN_DON
WEIGHT 1
VOLUME 1
SUBSTANCE CLOTH
*DESCRIPTION_START EXAMINE
Delicate fibers of different materials are woven together into this sash,
their combining making them stronger than they would be alone. The sash
is extremely comfortable and durable as a result.
*DESCRIPTION_END
VARIABLE praup
IFTOUCH -1
 IFVAR ORG ! 20
  ECHO PLAYER You feel many voices speak within your mind, "The Way is not open to you."
  ECHO OTHERS %N quickly pulls %h hand away from the sash.
 CLEARVERB
 ENDIF
 IFVAR INTNUM3 = 1
  ECHO PLAYER The variable for use is PRAUP.  If you @peek this at over 3, please make it 1.
 ENDIF
ENDIF
IFPREVERB PUSH -1
  CLEARVERB
  ADD praup 1
  IFVAR praup < 3
    IFVAR REGION = 0
      IFVAR INTNUM3 = 124
      ; Prophet (above)
        DISBAND
        ECHO PLAYER You raise your naginata to the sky, intoning the ancient Drakin words...you sense the power flow into you and then slowly transport you away...
        ECHO OTHERS %N raises his naginata to the sky...ancient words of Drakin are softly whispered by %i...swirling colors surround %i transporting %N far away...
        PLREVENT 3
