     ECHO PLAYER A gentle voice speaks in your mind, "Let not what happened in Tesinia darken your dreams. Let, instead, the knowledge of your triumph filter through your thoughts. And, remember always, that you are Dragonfriend."
     ECHO OTHERS %N rubs %h medallion, gently closing %h eyes.
   ENDIF
    IFVAR RAC = 2
     ECHO PLAYER A gentle voice speaks in your mind, "Let not the trust betrayed at Shemri's Grove haunt your dreams. Let, instead, the knowledge of your triumph ease your thoughts. And, remember always, that you are Dragonfriend."
     ECHO OTHERS %N rubs %h medallion, gently closing %h eyes.
