       ECHO OTHERs %N rubs %h medallion, gently closing %h eyes.
     ENDIF
      IFVAR RAC = 4
	ECHO PLAYER A gentle voice speaks in your mind, "Let not the defilers of the Pack Code make your dreams restless. Let, instead, the knowledge of your triumph ease your minds as you run with the wind and answer the call of the moon. And, remember always, that you are Dragonfriend."
	ECHO OTHERS %N rubs %h medallion, gently closing %h eyes.
      ENDIF
       IFVAR RAC = 6
	 ECHO PLAYER A gentle voice speaks in your mind, "Little cousin, the stains upon the honor of your race are not yours. Let not the memory of brother fighting brother darken your dreams. Let, instead, the knowledge that you upheld your Honor ease your mind. And, remember always, that you are Dragonfriend."
	 ECHO OTHERS %N rubs %h medallion, gently closing %h eyes.
       ENDIF
	IFVAR RAC = 7
	  ECHO PLAYER A gentle voice speaks in your mind, "You are sometimes called the least human of all the races, a machine made for killing. But, remember, when you were needed to save lives, you showed compassion beyond the ken of many of the more human races. And, remeber always, that you are Dragonfriend."
	  ECHO OTHERS %N rubs %h medallion, gently closing %h eyes.
	ENDIF
    ENDIF
ENDIF
