INUMBER 1709
NAME 866
MISC
WEIGHT 3
VOLUME 4
*DESCRIPTION_START EXAMINE
The lonriset resembles a mandolin in appearance, with a fretted neck
extending from a pear-shaped body. This particular instrument has been
crafted to perfection, with the ten silvery strings, dusted with diamonds,
sparkling reflectively off of the deeply polished rosewood that allows
each note played to resonate beautifully throughout the instrument. Painted
onto the fretted neck are intricate designs that flow, harmonically, around
the Royal Seal.
*DESCRIPTION_END
IFPREVERB PUSH -1
  CLEARVERB
  ECHO PLAYER You bring the lonriset close and strum a gentle melody that flows around you, filling your body with a soothing healing power.
  ECHO OTHERS %N brings the lonriset close and strums a gentle melody that flows around %i, imbuing %i with a comforting warmth.
  ROUTINE 1
ENDIF
IFPREVERB CARESS -1
  CLEARVERB
    ECHO PLAYER You hold the lonriset close and tune it for a moment before launching into your song. Your fingers flow over the strings, coaxing golden notes from the instrument, notes that hang in the air filling the area with enchanting music.
    ECHO OTHERS %N brings the lonriset close and tunes it for a moment before launching into %h song. %N's fingers flow effortlessly over the strings, coaxing golden notes from the instrument, notes that hang in the air filling the area with enchanting music.
ENDIF
IFPREVERB PULL -1
  CLEARVERB
    ECHO PLAYER Your fingers gently pluck at the strings, calling forth lyrical sounds that enhance the song emanating from deep within yourself.
    ECHO OTHERS Lyrical sounds emanate from the lonriset, as %N's fingers gently pluck at the strings, enhancing the enchanting song that flows from %h lips.
ENDIF
IFPREVERB KISS -1
  CLEARVERB
    ECHO PLAYER Your fingers weave a complex pattern over the finely-tuned strings of the lonriset as you bring your song to a close, letting the last few notes hang lazily in the air before they drift away...
    ECHO OTHERS %N's fingers weave a complex pattern over the finely-tuned strings of the lonriset as %s brings %h song to a close, letting the last few notes linger in the air before they gently fade away...
ENDIF
