	    IFVAR DUMMY5 = 3
	      ECHO PLAYER A gossamer faerie suddenly streaks by, leaving a trail of golden dust which settles in your hair.
	      ECHO OTHERS A gossamer fairie suddenly streaks by, leaving a trail of golden dust which settles into %N's hair.
	      SPELL 210
	    ENDIF
              IFVAR DUMMY5 = 4
                ECHO PLAYER Two faeries, their giggles sounding like no more than a breath of wind, massage your arms and then disappear.
                ECHO OTHERS Two faeries, their giggles sounding like no more than a breath of wind, massage %N's arms and then disappear.
                SPELL 209
              ENDIF
                IFVAR DUMMY5 = 5
                  ECHO PLAYER Landing on your head, a pretty little faerie leans over and kisses you on the forehead and vanishes.
                  ECHO OTHERS Landing on %N's head, a pretty little faerie leans over and kisses %N on the forehead and vanishes.
		  SPELL 102
                ENDIF
                  IFVAR DUMMY5 = 6
		    ECHO PLAYER A faerie, her emerald wings moving noiselessly, taps you on the shoulder and disappears in a swirl of color.
		    ECHO OTHERS A faerie, her emerald wings moving noiselessly, taps %N on the shoulder and disappears in a swirl of color.
		    SPELL 229
		  ENDIF
		    IFVAR DUMMY5 = 7
		      ECHO PLAYER The tiniest faerie you have ever seen suddenly appears, perching on the tip of your nose. She winks at you and then is gone.
		      ECHO OTHERS The tiniest faerie you have ever seen suddenly appears, perching on the tip of your nose. She winks at you and then is gone.
		      SPELL 234
		    ENDIF
		      IFVAR DUMMY5 = 8
			ECHO PLAYER You catch a glimpse of a faerie out of the corner of your eye as she whispers, "Poof!" in your ear.
			ECHO OTHERS You catch a glimpse of a faerie whispering something in %N's ear.
			SPELL 225
		      ENDIF
			IFVAR DUMMY5 = 9
			  ECHO PLAYER A ruby winged faerie flutters her wings softly against your cheek and then streaks out of sight.
			  ECHO OTHERS A ruby winged faerie flutters her wings softly against %N's cheek and then streaks out of sight.
			  SPELL 326
			ENDIF
			  IFVAR DUMMY5 = 10
			    ECHO PLAYER Laughing with sheer delight, a golden winged faerie does somersaults in your hair, vanishing as quickly as she appeared.
			    ECHO OTHERS Laughing with sheer delight, a golden winged faerie does somersaults in %N's hair, vanishing as quickly as she appeared.
			    SPELL 515
			  ENDIF
       ENDIF
	IFVAR ITEMVAL2 =< 0
	  ECHO PLAYER The pin sparkles and twinkles like the most brilliant of stars on a clear spring night.
	  ECHO OTHERS As %N touches %h faerie pin it sparkles and twinkles like the most brilliant of stars on a clear spring night.
	ENDIF
 ENDIF
