INUMBER 1451
NAME 902
MISC
WEIGHT 3
VOLUME 10
INTERIOR 10
CONTAINER ON
*DESCRIPTION_START
You see Solaria'Janus, an almost full grown female tigress. Her thick
snow-white fur glistens outlining her golden eyes and dark black nose.
Her enormous paws are heavily padded, her muscled body ripples with
strength and controlled power. A supple white leather collar studded with
diamonds from which hangs a white elkyri medallion cut in a diamond shape
with a blood-red slash across the front adorns her neck.
*DESCRIPTION_END
IFPREVERB RUB -1
	CLEARVERB
	ECHO ALL As %N leans over to stroke Solaria'Janus's sleek white coat the tigress lifts her massive head, rubbing her soft furry cheek against %N's hand.
ENDIF
IFPREVERB CARESS -1
	CLEARVERB
	ECHO ALL Solaria'Janus winds back and forth through %N's legs, rubbing affectionately against %i.
ENDIF
IFPREVERB HUG -1
	CLEARVERB
	ECHO ALL When %N wraps %h arms around Solaria'Janus's neck giving her a big hug the white tigress lays her massive head on %N's shoulder, nearly knocking %N over.
ENDIF
IFPREVERB KISS -1
	CLEARVERB
	ECHO ALL Solaria'Janus suddenly stands on her two hind legs, places her huge paws on %N's shoulder and draws her tongue slowly over %N's face in a big wet kiss.
ENDIF
IFPREVERB NIBBLE -1
	CLEARVERB
	ECHO ALL Playfully placing her paws on one of %N's feet, Solaria'Janus proceeds to gnaw gently on %N's ankle.
ENDIF
IFPREVERB PUSH -1
	CLEARVERB
	RANDOM dummy1 1 4 0
	IFVAR dummy1 = 1
		ECHO ALL Solaria'Janus bounds out of view, stalking some imaginary prey, then pads silently back into the room and sits warily at %N's side.
	ENDIF
	IFVAR dummy1 = 2
		ECHO ALL Solaria'Janus emits a low growl as her body tenses. With an enormous leap she pounces on something, grasping it in her huge jaws. Proudly striding back to %N she drops the object in %N's lap.
	ENDIF
	IFVAR dummy1 = 3
		ECHO ALL Standing protectively at %N's side Solaria'Janus scans the area, her lips raised in a threatening snarl.
	ENDIF
	IFVAR dummy1 = 4
		ECHO ALL Solaria'Janus's ears perk up, her gaze directed at something in the distance. With a few agile strides she slips from view only to quickly return with a satisfied look in her eyes.
	ENDIF
ENDIF
IFPREVERB CUDDLE -1
	CLEARVERB
	ECHO ALL Solaria'Janus politely lays her head on %N's arm then suddenly leaps up, trying to squirm her way into %N's lap, knocking %N onto the ground.
	POSITION SIT
ENDIF
IFPREVERB PULL -1
	CLEARVERB
	ECHO ALL %N takes Solaria'Janus by the scruff of the neck.
ENDIF
IFPREVERB TURN -1
	CLEARVERB
	ECHO ALL Arching her back, Solaria'Janus stretches and yawns, her white fangs glistening as her tail swishes lazily back and forth.
ENDIF
IFPREVERB THUMP -1
	CLEARVERB
	ECHO ALL %N thumps Solaria'Janus on the head!
ENDIF
IFPREVERB POKE -1
	CLEARVERB
	ECHO ALL Extending her razor sharp claws, Solaria'Janus bats playfully at a dustball swirling in the wind.
ENDIF
IFPREVERB WAVE -1
	CLEARVERB
	ECHO ALL As %N tries to lift Solaria'Janus into the air, she quickly backs away hissing and spitting at %N.
ENDIF
IFPREVERB DEPOSIT -1
	CLEARVERB
	ECHO ALL The bank teller says, "Sorry, %N, but there isn't room for a tiger in your safety deposit box."
ENDIF
IFPREVERB TICKLE -1
	CLEARVERB
	ECHO ALL Trying to keep her regal composure, Solaria'Janus rolls over onto her stomach and nudges %N, asking to have her tummy rubbed.
ENDIF
IFPREVERB TOUCH -1
	CLEARVERB
	ECHO ALL The huge white tigress purrs softly, rubbing affectionately against %N.
ENDIF
IFPREVERB PUNCH -1
	CLEARVERB
	ECHO ALL %N punches Solaria'Janus!
ENDIF
IFPREVERB SNIFF -1
	CLEARVERB
	ECHO ALL Solaria'Janus curiously sniffs %N, wiggling her long black whiskers.
ENDIF
IFPREVERB KICK -1
	CLEARVERB
	ECHO ALL %N gives Solaria'Janus a swift kick!
ENDIF
IFPREVERB TAP -1
	CLEARVERB
	ECHO ALL Raising her beautiful head, Solaria'Janus looks at %N questioningly.
ENDIF
IFVERB GROWL -1
	ECHO ALL Answering %N's growl, Solaria'Janus softly growls back.
ENDIF
IFVERB SNARL -1
	ECHO ALL Lifting her head slightly, Solaria'Janus bares her teeth and snarls at %N.
ENDIF
IFVERB PET -1
	ECHO ALL Solaria'Janus gazes affectionately at %N, leaning against %h leg and flicking her tongue out over %N's hand.
ENDIF
IFVERB LISTEN -1
	ECHO ALL Solaria'Janus purrs as a gentle growl emanates deep from within her throat.
ENDIF
IFVERB WHISTLE -1
	RANDOM dummy2 1 3 0
	IFVAR dummy2 = 1
		ECHO ALL Solaria'Janus glaces over at %N, then indifferently looks away, ignoring %i.
	ENDIF
	IFVAR dummy2 = 2
		ECHO ALL Seeming to nod at %N, Solaria'Janus moves right up against %i and waits at attention.
	ENDIF
	IFVAR dummy2 = 3
		ECHO ALL Solaria'Janus's ears perk up as she starts to move towards %N. Suddenly she stops and seems more concerned with cleaning her face.
	ENDIF
ENDIF
IFPREVERB LEAN -1
	CLEARVERB
	ECHO ALL Leaning with her full weight against %N, Solaria'Janus flicks her tail as she watches %N topple over.
	POSITION LAY
ENDIF
IFPREVERB SPIT -1
	CLEARVERB
	ECHO ALL Solaria'Janus rears up on her hind feet, closing %N's head within her huge jaws, gently shaking %i back and forth before dropping %i to the ground.
	POSITION LAY
ENDIF
IFPREVERB2 PUT -1
	CLEARVERB
	IFVAR ARCHNUM = 790
		REMOVEITEM -1
		ECHO ALL Solaria'Janus tentatively licks the cookie and then quickly devours it, licking her huge jaws.
	ENDIF
ENDIF
IFPREVERB2 PUT -1
	CLEARVERB
	IFVAR ARCHNUM = 455
		REMOVEITEM -1
		ECHO ALL Nosing the mutton, Solaria'Janus grips it between her teeth, tearing it and gulping it down.
	ENDIF
ENDIF
