FOOD
PARAMETER1 2
IFPREVERB READ -1
 IFVAR INTNUM3 = 1
   ECHO PLAYER %c*** THIS LETTER IS MEANT FOR
   ECHO PLAYER     JOE (INTNUM 117) AS A ROLE
   ECHO PLAYER     PLAYING DEVICE. DO NOT USE   ***%c
 ENDIF
  IFVAR RAC = 2
     ECHO OTHERS %n quickly reads %a.
     CLEARVERB
     ECHO PLAYER      %cMy son, I make preparations to call forth the power of change.
     ECHO PLAYER Tonight the very sky shall yield as I invoke my power. But enough, I
     ECHO PLAYER write to warn you things will not be pleasant tonight, for it seems I
     ECHO PLAYER have been slightly outwitted. So take my warning and make youself
     ECHO PLAYER scarce. Meet beneath the gray oak at tomorrows twilight.
     ECHO PLAYER                                 Tilikious.%c
  ELSE
    ECHO PLAYER The text is written in a language foreign to you.
    CLEARVERB
  ENDIF
ENDIF
